Rochelle Hudson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rochelle_Hudson 0 Rochelle Elizabeth Hudson (March 6, 1916 – January 17, 1972) was an American film actress from the 1930s through the 1960s. Hudson was a WAMPAS Baby Star in 1931. Rochelle_Elizabeth_Hudson ( March_6_,_1916 – January_17_,_1972 ) was an_American_film_actress from the_1930s through the_1960s .
